The paper also proposes a novel optimization method, which falls under the category of optimization algorithms, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a likely sub-category as well. Finally, the paper discusses the potential impact of their method on system-level optimization, which could fall under the category of control and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible sub-category.
